### Traversing


## Children Node

```js  
// Select first child of body
let first = document.body.children[0];
//  Reassign Text 
first.innerHTML = 'BROWN BEARS ARE AWESOME!';

```


## Parent Node

```js  
//  Select Child Node
const child = document.getElementById('firstItem');

//  Select Parent Node from that CHildren
const orderedList = child.parentNode; 

```
